    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Cavalier/Samurai Banner</strong><br/><br/><p>These grim fetishes are common among Jadwiga cavaliers. An ally who benefits from this standard gains a +1 bonus on caster level checks to bypass spell resistance and a +1 bonus to the DC of her hexes and necromancy or enchantment spell she casts. At 10th level and every 5 levels thereafter, the bonus on caster level checks increases by 1. At 14th level, an ally benefiting from the banner gains a +2 morale bonus on saving throws against spells or effects that deal hit point damage. When the cavalier or samurai waves this standard, a number of allies equal to the cavalier or samurai's Charisma modifier (minimum 1) within 60 feet can attempt an Intimidate check to demoralize a foe as an immediate action.</p>",
